description:
This market will resolve to "Yes" if Captain of the National Team for England Harry Kane is the top goalscorer in the FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

If Harry Kane ties for top goalscorer in the FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022, this market will still resolve to "Yes".

If FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 has not ended by December 31, 2022, 11:59:59 PM ET, this market will resolve according to the statistics already available.

The primary resolution source for this market will be official information from FIFA (e.g. https://www.fifa.com/fifaplus/en/tournaments/mens/worldcup/qatar2022/scores-fixtures), including official footage from the World Cup, however a consensus of credible reporting may also be used.
